01:30:56,185 --> 01:31:06,249
[SPEAKER_10]: And the reason it wasn't, you know, the reason that it wasn't like we didn't have anything brought up at this meeting is basically because of the timelines that our consultants work in.

881
01:31:06,329 --> 01:31:14,473
[SPEAKER_10]: So if Tufts gives like a list of bullet points on, I believe it was April 16th or 17th when they sent it to us,

882
01:31:15,013 --> 01:31:25,459
