884
01:31:41,028 --> 01:31:43,390
[SPEAKER_10]: I will say that in that conversation there was

885
01:31:44,110 --> 01:32:04,047
[SPEAKER_10]: sort of like there was this sense of like you know any like we're not going to be having like like like this this is a one-time thing we're not going to be like having a bunch of these like secret conversation with Tufts folks if you're going to like if you're going to like tell us what you want yes you do need to like write it down and then give it to us and then that will be made public

886
01:32:05,487 --> 01:32:17,192
[SPEAKER_10]: So yeah, I would say that a lot of the back and forth was that, and a lot of the delays in getting the Tufts institutional zone was because of that sort of process.

887
01:32:17,232 --> 01:32:22,414
[SPEAKER_10]: It was because the rezoning process did kind of blow up.

888
01:32:24,775 --> 01:32:49,422
[SPEAKER_10]: um last year and i have a lot to say on that um but we are trying to like be but we are like earnestly trying to be as nice as we as we uh can to anybody who like wants to work with us um to as possible and so yes we're gonna we are gonna like take a meeting with them we're gonna like have a conversation hear them out but there's not going to be this pattern of like

889
01:32:51,343 --> 01:32:53,044
[SPEAKER_10]: behind the scenes conversations.

890
01:32:53,505 --> 01:33:00,410
[SPEAKER_10]: Anything that Tufts want is going to be and will be public at the end of the day.

891
01:33:00,430 --> 01:33:06,135
[SPEAKER_10]: I hope that offers some clarity of the behind the scenes aspect of all of this.

892
01:33:13,327 --> 01:33:38,534
[SPEAKER_10]: I will say that the way that the schedule is sort of set up, and the reason that we're sort of having these other public information sessions again is because, you know, we were being, like, there was a lot of criticism last year of, like, not being open enough about these things, not being, like, not having, like, enough outreach to the public.

893
01:33:38,574 --> 01:33:42,035
[SPEAKER_10]: So yeah, we're having two public information sessions on this.

894
01:33:42,895 --> 01:33:45,257
[SPEAKER_10]: and I wanted them to be scheduled ahead of time.

895
01:33:45,377 --> 01:33:51,421
[SPEAKER_10]: One of them on April 30th and the other is going to be on June 1st to kind of invite folks from the neighborhood.

896
01:33:51,441 --> 01:34:01,128
[SPEAKER_10]: And I understand that that means, unfortunately, some folks will be coming in that have already come to many of these meetings and will be saying the same things.

