964
01:41:57,383 --> 01:42:14,332
[SPEAKER_06]: I really liked the idea of coming to the meeting on the 30th with some sort of summary from what we heard about from the work next spring, but also do want to acknowledge the point that we may have people who are showing up there for the very first time.

965
01:42:14,412 --> 01:42:22,776
[SPEAKER_06]: So we will have a review of both the Boston Avenue and the Tufts area, and we're going to recombine the presentation.

966
01:42:23,178 --> 01:42:24,258
[SPEAKER_06]: to address both of those.

967
01:42:24,578 --> 01:42:27,739
[SPEAKER_06]: Just want to confirm that that's what we're looking for for the next meeting.

968
01:42:28,259 --> 01:42:31,920
